welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Keles, the charming city known for its beautiful architecture and rich cultural heritage. We invite you to immerse yourself in our vibrant community and discover all the wonders our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tashkent International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal dedicated to international flights, primarily used by Uzbekistan Airways.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: A newly built terminal for domestic flights, with modern facilities and amenities.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, but may require a password from the information desk.
